name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-wake-island-2007
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 9 survey sites at Wake Island in the Pacific Remote Island Areas in April 30 to May 3, 2007 from the NOAA vessel Hi'ialakai (Cruise ID HI0701). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
